{"tid":1846874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人已經入晒黎, 醫護仲應唔應該罷工?","createTime":"2020-01-27T18:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T18:52:02.000Z","uid":28068,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9fae9a096318e58e02b2d3e1ef61121743c02d17","tid":1846874,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:35:59.000Z","msg":"罷, 要求將所有支那人送番大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔罷, 誓死求所有支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全港繼續大罷工呀!!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4a43e56810a03a78f12df30dc63390e5c7b901d2","tid":1846874,"uid":329466,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:36:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔罷工既醫護就係賣港賊 罪名同黑警一樣 唔好同我講話尊重醫護決定 為左光環囉香港人黎陪大陸狗 食屎喇</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ed303039778dd6cbe7da88974f30b06b6c1eb80b","tid":1846874,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"唔支持罷工既我dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝你全家生肺炎"},{"pid":"0dc1c2a6e3716d8bf7b3dce6aca5aa23a26b102f","tid":1846874,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d806b38405d602c9c09bc8f03834043bc22500","tid":1846874,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:37:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0ea7f9248464a6b552525a20453f1d5f455f906","tid":1846874,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:39:32.000Z","msg":"黎明行動送頭<br />\n港島遊行集會送頭<br />\n深夜整連儂牆送頭<br />\n派傳單都會畀藍絲割肚不了<br />\n<br />\n而家我哋打旗號叫政府封關阻肺炎呀<br />\n民建聯都唔會夠膽出聲反對啦 粉嶺單野政府都hea應啦<br />\n<br />\n另外想問工會過咗咁多個月有幾多人入咗會？<br />\n全民大三罷？<br />\n唔好話無限期啦 就算一日 短期內我都睇唔出我哋有咩條件做得到 到時幾多生化人入咗關？再搞無限期三罷已經遲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為到時已經有唔少香港人奶咗野 咁醫護仲點罷工呀</span><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦送頭<br />\n你話畀我知唔送頭仲可以點"},{"pid":"126d72a6f7483d2755c70621c122a43ecee6e96e","tid":1846874,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:40:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻政權</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f261c683a5a350df1761091e1ef2155d65a2dc1","tid":1846874,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:41:41.000Z","msg":"講個笑話<br />\n香港人罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smi